    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_8DA45F50-22D1-0135-9AA2-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The public course index is a collection of all courses in your institution that can be viewed publicly. In relation to the index, the word public references the index, not the courses; courses in the index may be public or private courses. Learn how to view the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-view-my-institution-s-Public-Course-Index-as-an/ta-p/706" target="_blank">Public Course Index</a>.</p>
<p>If you want to include your course as part of the public course index, you can select the course index visibility option in course settings. You can also create a description for your course as part of the catalog listing.</p>
<p>To learn more about visibility options, view the <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/t5/Canvas-Resource-Documents/Canvas-Course-Visibility-Options/ta-p/387053" target="_blank">Canvas Course Visibility Options resource document</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Notes</strong>: </p>
<ul>
<li>The Public Course Index is currently an <a href="/t5/Admin-Guide/How-do-I-set-details-for-an-account/ta-p/194" target="_blank">account setting</a> and must be enabled by your institutional admin. </li>
<li>If your course is enabled for self-enrollment, you can <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-enable-course-self-enrollment-with-a-join-code-or/ta-p/830" target="_blank">add a Join button</a> to allow users to self-enroll at any time. This option does not have to be enabled to include a course in the Public Course Index, but students who view the course will not be able to contribute to any discussions, quizzes, or assignments unless they are enrolled.</li>
<li>If a course includes an end date, the course is not automatically removed from the Public Course Index.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_settings" data-step-uuid="3cffbf91-c72d-4fa6-afc5-7970d2d5734b">
