      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="set_visibility" data-step-uuid="5ffa8cb8-a43c-45bf-95bd-02f9cbc70b10">
    <h2 id="set_visibility" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Set Visibility</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/832/556/original/caebc9b5-2bb5-424d-b22a-189226f8592f.png" srcset="" alt="Set Visibility" height="184" width="488">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_8DA5C0C0-22D1-0135-9AA8-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the visibility options, click the <strong>Include this course in the public course index</strong> checkbox.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

